headline: Brokers Suggest Investing in Arch Capital (ACGL): Read This Before Placing a Bet
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Arch Capital (ACGL) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?
